{"tid":415672,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打玩開賽車game?","createTime":"2017-09-27T07:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T12:20:55.000Z","uid":118865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8263fc39cfa0acba7f39e4feabc314ca9423ddb6","tid":415672,"uid":118865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:21:08.000Z","msg":"基本上玩賽車game係咪玩pc比較好 <br />\n我上網睇人玩pc 可以下載唔同既賽道玩 <br />\n缺點係多數賽車都係英文為主 例子就好似ASSETTO CORSA<br />\n入GAME前個SETTING 永遠都唔知點搞好 對車認識又唔大<br />\n而且自己部PC主要文書用 都唔會諗住打到機  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n家用機就每出一部新既 每次要交學費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n雖然最近九月出左其他賽車GAME <br />\n但好少賽車GAME有頭文字D/灣岸既感覺,主要偏向真實感<br />\n上年頭文字D 十週年 枉我期望有好消息 但最後都係唔撚出移植版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到自己留左部PS3 得閒玩下頭文字D <br />\n如果你肯移D6AA 都好足夠   反正你動漫果D都做哂<br />\n街機你出到ZERO都唔知你仲會唔會出到新一系列<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打準備/已買邊幾款車GAME???有無咩好推介<br />\n始終係香港玩賽車GAME既人比較少  偏向歐洲人多<br />\n<br />\n用開G29 但有D GAME直情唔支援G29<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時GT SPORT就訂左 但其餘既仲未吸引到自己買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1831c4af8f0adf3c2cefd21da012dbb41c19d5e5","tid":415672,"uid":37107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"唔熟車最好唔好玩assetto corsa 太複雜<br />\n仲有 logi既軚盤係垃圾"},{"pid":"f141d23e98cd3da31ea347c21e3e20bc9accd27d","tid":415672,"uid":118865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔熟車最好唔好玩assetto corsa 太複雜<br />\n仲有 logi既軚盤係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n始終家用機選擇少  <br />\n有錢 一係上T500RS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  雖然個波棍的確好吸引"},{"pid":"920522553e2f5f090e1737f6bb35af63ef5c83e6","tid":415672,"uid":33694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T07:30:35.000Z","msg":"啱啱買咗t300rs gt 同th8a<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"